  "text": "It is interesting to note that in both cases our results are identical to those of [CITATION_1] , but in the FDR based selection procedures there is no need to estimate parameters via bootstrapping, and therefore, they are faster and easier to implement. In fact, as noted in Introduction, any user of standard statistical software can use them.",
